      <long>
         <en><![CDATA[This is a GLPI plugin that facilitates single sign on authentication with an identity provider using the SAML 2.0 protocol. This tool leverages the Onelogin PHP library. Tested with ADFS 2.0+, Google IDP and Azure AD. You can find installation instructions at plugin homepage.<br/><br/>Changelog:<br/><br/> 2015.12:<br/><br/> - plugin is now compatible with GLPI 0.90<br/><br/>2017.05:<br/><br/>- plugin is now compatible with GLPI 9.1.3<br/><br/>2021.01:<br/><br/>- Version 1.1 release<br/><br/><a href="https://github.com/derricksmith/phpsaml">PHP SAML on Github</a>]]></en>
      </long>
